  "body": "### Component\n\nForge\n\n### Describe the feature you would like\n\nIn https://github.com/foundry-rs/forge-std/pull/229 we hardcode some common addresses test suites may encounter. From a quick test it seems the VM, console, and create2deployer addresses are already labeled in traces, but the default sender and correspond default test contract address are not labeled, but should be\r\n\r\n```solidity\r\n// Default address for tx.origin and msg.sender, 0x1804c8AB1F12E6bbf3894d4083f33e07309d1f38.\r\naddress internal constant DEFAULT_SENDER = address(uint160(uint256(keccak256(\"foundry default caller\"))));\r\n\r\n// Address of the test contract, deployed by the DEFAULT_SENDER.\r\naddress internal constant TEST_CONTRACT = 0x5615dEB798BB3E4dFa0139dFa1b3D433Cc23b72f;\r\n```\n\n### Additional context\n\n_No response_",
